data.description: Beautifully updated 2-bedroom (plus bonus 3rd room), 2-bathroom home in Eden Pines Colony.  Open concept floor plan with upgraded kitchen, plenty of cabinet space, large pantry and new stainless-steel appliances.  Two spacious bedrooms plus a bonus room which is currently being used as an office.  Two full bathrooms; one off the master.  Screened front porch, fully fenced lot with plenty of room for parking. Low-maintenance landscaping with storage shed.  Extra privacy as lot next door is County owned.  Boat ramp conveniently located nearby.  Assumable flood insurance policy.
